Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Vessels' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
And 'Varicosis' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Aneurysm' radio button
Then 'Common iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'External iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Internal iliac artery' radio button is enabled
And 'Common femoral artery' radio button is enabled

And 'Max. axial diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Craniocaudal extension' input field is enabled

When I select 'Varicosis' radio button
Then 'Iliac veins' checkbox is enabled
And 'Superficial leg veins' checkbox is enabled
And 'Deep leg veinss' checkbox is enabled
